title: Listening To The Whisper | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Listening To The Whisper | Joel Osteen
description:
God places gentle promptings in our spirits to guide us. When you hear that still, small voice, that’s Him leading you down the best path for your life.  

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
